title: Thunderdome Demo - Part II
tags: 2014 AtariST Compowinner Demo SillyVenture video YM
info: Track for the Thunderdome Demo released by Checkpoint at Silly Venture 2014. Something a bit different, with simple instrument design, YM drums, no DMA, and very few SID voices to meet the demo constraints. Congrats to Checkpoint for the 1st place !
